When you sit here...

511
00:34:27,024 --> 00:34:28,025
But it won't.

512
00:34:28,651 --> 00:34:30,694
You will eat their shit.

513
00:34:31,820 --> 00:34:34,156
Daniels, too, when he gets here.

514
00:34:51,215 --> 00:34:53,455
