534
00:36:11,211 --> 00:36:14,006
Shit, I don't even remember
what was in that file.

535
00:36:14,089 --> 00:36:16,717
Something about the eastern district.

536
00:36:17,468 --> 00:36:19,094
So long ago,

537
00:36:19,178 --> 00:36:20,679
