586
00:38:59,963 --> 00:39:03,133
Nowadays, all they care about
is a goddamn video.

587
00:39:04,843 --> 00:39:08,347
- They've forgotten.
- I don't know why we're doing this.

588
00:39:08,430 --> 00:39:10,724
I can write a report like this in my sleep.

589
00:39:10,807 --> 00:39:13,810
There's no way Jay checks what I'm doing.

590
00:39:13,894 --> 00:39:16,396
Jimmy, Jimmy, a lot rides on this.

591
