it'll read like a real case.

593
00:39:21,944 --> 00:39:24,029
I was in the squad room today,

594
00:39:24,112 --> 00:39:26,782
all the casework laid out
like I'm lost in a career case.

595
00:39:26,865 --> 00:39:29,201
- Landsman barely noticed.
- We crank this up,

596
00:39:29,284 --> 00:39:31,954
landsman won't be the only one
thumbing through this h-file.

597
00:39:32,704 --> 00:39:35,624
