Maybe later. I got to get ready for work.

602
00:40:22,421 --> 00:40:25,173
- Does your dog bite?
- Got teeth, don't he?

603
00:40:26,341 --> 00:40:28,594
Chip change, get your
ass in here. That's it.

604
00:40:29,428 --> 00:40:31,513
I'm detective mcnulty, homicide.

605
00:40:31,597 --> 00:40:33,557
Can I ask you a few questions?

606
00:40:33,640 --> 00:40:36,351
Got a card? Hey!

607
00:40:39,605 --> 00:40:41,189
