I'm gonna ask you once, where Joe?

613
00:41:50,801 --> 00:41:52,844
Skip past the talking.

614
00:41:52,928 --> 00:41:55,180
Do what you feel.

615
00:41:55,263 --> 00:41:56,932
Joe ain't had nothing to do with...

616
