Now, slim, you gonna make me hurt you, yo.

617
00:42:01,645 --> 00:42:05,190
Ask yourself, dog,
why would Joe give butchie up?

618
00:42:08,110 --> 00:42:10,195
If marlo could make him talk,

619
00:42:10,278 --> 00:42:12,614
he puts Joe inside your big score.

620
00:42:13,156 --> 00:42:16,868
If Joe turned butchie, I'd tell you.

621
00:42:16,952 --> 00:42:19,371
Shit, I help you, even.

622
00:42:19,454 --> 00:42:21,081
But it just ain't like that.

623
