Come on, yo.

624
00:42:27,462 --> 00:42:28,588
Finish it.

625
00:42:56,116 --> 00:42:58,076
Take a look at the fifth graph.

626
00:42:58,160 --> 00:43:02,581
"The mayor," comma, "incensed by
the commissioner's performance..."

627
00:43:02,664 --> 00:43:04,875
- "Incensed" seems over the top.
- I don't know.

628
00:43:04,958 --> 00:43:08,503
Drug legalization fiasco,
the bodies in the vacants,

629
00:43:08,587 --> 00:43:10,839
