634
00:43:26,688 --> 00:43:28,607
Galled, vexed, annoyed...

635
00:43:28,690 --> 00:43:30,859
Safer still... displeased.

636
00:43:31,359 --> 00:43:33,153
You'd take the crab out of crab soup.

637
00:43:37,365 --> 00:43:41,036
Hey, Scott, that was good work
by you and zorzi catching us up.

638
00:43:41,328 --> 00:43:43,872
- Great effort.
- There's an "attaboy" for you.

639
00:43:45,540 --> 00:43:47,042
How'd it go in Washington?

640
00:43:48,376 --> 00:43:49,586
Buyer's market out there.

641
00:43:54,216 --> 00:43:56,343
Baltimore sun ain't so bad.

642
00:43:57,469 --> 00:43:59,638
9-Adam-4-3.

643
00:43:59,721 --> 00:44:01,097
43.

644
00:44:01,181 --> 00:44:04,810
Reported doa, alley in the rear
