645
00:44:04,893 --> 00:44:07,312
Copy doa.

646
00:44:07,395 --> 00:44:11,900
9-46. K-g-a, advise 43
I'm close by. I'll handle it.

647
00:44:11,983 --> 00:44:13,944
Copy, 9-Adam-46.

648
00:44:14,986 --> 00:44:20,325
Bunk, are you feeling all right?
She said "doa", not "donut".

649
