653
00:44:55,902 --> 00:44:56,903
Right?

654
00:45:04,160 --> 00:45:06,288
Man already shit hisself,

655
00:45:06,371 --> 00:45:08,623
and we ain't even get started yet.

656
00:45:08,707 --> 00:45:10,458
He's funky, yo.

657
