I know him. Avon's lawyer.

670
00:46:14,314 --> 00:46:17,567
Yeah, mine, too. Brick uses him.

671
00:46:17,651 --> 00:46:21,696
So does Phil boy for most of his stuff,
not just the criminal side.

672
00:46:21,780 --> 00:46:26,117
