674
00:46:28,620 --> 00:46:30,538
This where you need to be.

675
00:46:32,165 --> 00:46:34,459
Joseph, you're looking prosperous.

676
00:46:34,542 --> 00:46:36,461
I get by.

677
00:46:36,544 --> 00:46:37,545
Mr. Stanfield.

678
