683
00:47:18,878 --> 00:47:21,172
Carcetti finally dumps burrell.

684
00:47:22,215 --> 00:47:24,759
Ervin was a year before me at dunbar.

685
00:47:26,052 --> 00:47:27,053
No shit.

686
00:47:28,596 --> 00:47:30,306
He was in the glee club.

687
00:47:33,768 --> 00:47:35,186
You're killing me. I got to ask.

688
00:47:35,270 --> 00:47:36,312
Stone stupid.

689
00:47:43,028 --> 00:47:45,613
Elijah? Say hi to aunt kima.

690
00:47:51,619 --> 00:47:53,913
Anyways, you were right on time with this.

691
00:47:53,997 --> 00:47:56,207
I got a dozen things to get done,

692
00:47:56,291 --> 00:47:59,044
and I got to do them
while working overtime at the station.

693
00:47:59,127 --> 00:48:01,212
- Been busy, huh?
- Yeah. Your boss got fired.

694
00:48:01,296 --> 00:48:02,964
We've been running ever since.

695
00:48:05,050 --> 00:48:06,176
Bye, lij.

696
00:48:07,302 --> 00:48:08,970
Go on. We'll be fine.

697
00:48:18,271 --> 00:48:19,898
Wow, that's good.

698
00:48:20,190 --> 00:48:21,983
You staying inside the lines.

699
00:48:27,197 --> 00:48:28,406
Hey, you want to do something?

700
00:48:30,075 --> 00:48:31,326
Go to the park?

701
00:48:32,994 --> 00:48:34,370
Get some ice cream?

702
