716
00:50:16,264 --> 00:50:19,851
I mean, I know you got rank now,
you're damn near lieutenant, but still...

717
00:50:21,853 --> 00:50:23,813
It ain't about the rank.

718
00:50:28,109 --> 00:50:29,861
I never told you, herc.

719
00:50:31,738 --> 00:50:33,781
Never said a fucking word.

720
00:50:34,741 --> 00:50:38,453
But when I gave you that kid
to debrief last year, whatshisface?

721
00:50:38,536 --> 00:50:40,872
You were supposed to get him
to bunk moreland. Remember?

722
00:50:42,165 --> 00:50:45,501
Yeah. I fucked up. So what?

723
00:50:46,711 --> 00:50:48,296
So it mattered.

724
00:50:49,297 --> 00:50:51,716
What the fuck does this
have to do with colicchio?

725
00:50:51,799 --> 00:50:55,720
It all matters.
I know we thought it didn't, but...

726
00:50:58,473 --> 00:50:59,807
It does.

727
00:51:03,603 --> 00:51:05,855
So you got to do colicchio, huh?

728
00:51:07,065 --> 00:51:09,275
Guess you think they had to do me.

729
00:51:12,654 --> 00:51:14,239
Yeah, probably.

730
00:51:18,076 --> 00:51:20,912
